<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <title>Lorem Generator</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1">
  <meta property="og:image" content="/images/logo.png" />
  <meta property="og:title" content="Lorem Generator" />
  <meta property="og:site_name" content="Lorem Generator" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="A wise, if not slightly pedantic, generator of metaphor." />
  <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
  <script type="text/javascript" src="/js/jquery-2.0.3.js" defer></script>
  <script type="text/javascript" src="/js/site.js" defer></script>
  <link rel='stylesheet' href='/css/style.css' />
  <link rel='stylesheet' href='/css/bootstrap.min.css' />
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container> text-center">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="block">
        <div class="title section">
          <img data-name="title" src="/images/logo.png" alt="LOGO" height="72" width="72">
          <h3 data-name="title">Metaphorpsum</h3>
          <p>Click above to generate a random paragraph</p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-center">Scroll down to continue reading for more information on usage
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="block white">
        <div class="metaphor section">
          <blockquote>
            <p class="metaphor-text">
              <%= sentences %>
            </p>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="block">
        <div class="generate section clearfix">
          <h3>Options</h3>
          <p>Give me <input type="text" class="number" data-name="paragraphs" value="2" maxlength="2" /> paragraph(s)
            containing <input type="text" class="number" data-name="sentences" value="4" maxlength="2" /> sentence(s)
            each; <select class="p-tags" data-name="p-tags">
              <option value="0" selected>do not</option>
              <option value="1">please</option>
            </select> wrap them in &lt;p&gt; tags.</p>
          <button class="button float" data-name="generate">Generate</button>
          <p id="error" class="text-red float">Huh? Numbers please. Above 0.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="block red">
        <div class="usage section">
          <h3>API Usage</h3>
          <div class="text-block">
            <p>Get paragraphs by sending an AJAX request to</p>
            <p><a href="/paragraphs/2">lorem.casjay.coffee/paragraphs/&lt;numberOfParagraphs&gt;</a></p>
            <p><a
                href="/paragraphs/2/4">lorem.casjay.coffee/paragraphs/&lt;numberOfParagraphs&gt;/&lt;numberOfSentences&gt;</a>
            </p>
            <p>limit: 20 paragraphs / 50 sentences</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-block">
            <p>Or just grab a few sentences by hitting</p>
            <p><a href="/sentences/5">lorem.casjay.coffee/sentences/&lt;numberOfSentences&gt;</a></p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-block">
            <p>Add a URL parameter p=true to get each paragraph in &lt;p&gt; tags</p>
            <p><a href="/paragraphs/3?p=true">lorem.casjay.coffee/paragraphs/3?p=true</a></p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-block">
            <p>Using OS X or Linux? Try this in the command line:</p>
            <p class="text-color">curl -q -LSs http://lorem.casjay.coffee/sentences/3</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-block clearfix">
            <p>And here’s a nifty MacOS bash script that copies metaphorpsum straight to your clipboard</p>
            <p class="text-color">
              function lorem() { curl -q -LSs http://lorem.casjay.coffee/sentences/${@:-5} | pbcopy ;}
            </p>
            <p>And here’s a nifty Linux bash script that copies metaphorpsum straight to your clipboard</p>
            <p class="text-color">
              function lorem() { curl -q -LSs http://lorem.casjay.coffee/sentences/${@:-5} | xclip -selection clipboard
              ;}
            </p>
            <p>usage: <span class=" text-color">lorem 10</span></p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-block">
            <p>Using <a href="http://www.alfredapp.com/">Alfred</a>? There's a workflow for that.</p>
            <p><a
                href="https://github.com/ColeTownsend/metaphor-ipsum-workflow">https://github.com/ColeTownsend/metaphor-ipsum-workflow</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="block">
        <div class="credits section section--short">
          <p>Built by <a href="http://kylestetz.com">Kyle Stetz</a> and maintained by
            <a href="http://casjay.info">Jason Hempstead</a>
            <br />Get the source code on <a href="https://github.com/now-sh/lorem">GitHub</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>
